cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.CL 

This paper deals with pruning deep CNN models, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also proposes a novel method for pruning with limited data, which falls under the category of artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The use of residual connections is also a key aspect of the paper, which is a popular technique in neural networks (cs.NE) and natural language processing (cs.CL).
